file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Prime Developer Trial
  version: v1
servers:
- url: https://api.factset.com/wealth/v1
security:
- FactSetApiKey: []
- FactSetOAuth2: []
tags:
- description: recommendationList endpoints
  name: recommendationList
paths:
  /recommendationList/get:
    get:
      description: Attributes of a single list, including data about its active revision.
      operationId: get/recommendationList/get
      parameters:
      - description: Identifier of the list.
        in: query
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        x-positive: true
      - description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
          set.
        explode: false
        in: query
        name: _attributes
        schema:
          items:
            maxLength: 100
            type: string
          maxItems: 50
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
        style: form
      - description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
        in: query
        name: _language
        schema:
          exclusiveMaximum: false
          exclusiveMinimum: false
          format: isoLanguage
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: Attributes of a single list.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-accepts: application/json
  /recommendationList/search:
    get:
      description: Search for recommendation lists, delivering an array of recommendation
        lists matching the specified filter criteria. The data provided for each recommendation
        list includes the currently active revision (or null in case no active revision
        exists).
      operationId: get/recommendationList/search
      parameters:
      - description: Restricts the search to recommendation lists, which contain the
          provided string in their name attribute. The filter is a case-insensitive
          substring match.
        in: query
        name: name
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Restrict the search to recommendation lists, which are currently
          active (e.g., current date is before the recommendation list's activeRange.end
          date). If set to false, recommendation lists will be returned regardless
          of their state.
        in: query
        name: onlyActive
        schema:
          type: boolean
      - description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
          set.
        explode: false
        in: query
        name: _attributes
        schema:
          items:
            maxLength: 100
            type: string
          maxItems: 50
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
        style: form
      - description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
        in: query
        name: _language
        schema:
          exclusiveMaximum: false
          exclusiveMinimum: false
          format: isoLanguage
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_1'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: Search for recommendation lists.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-accepts: application/json
  /recommendationList/revision/get:
    get:
      description: Attributes of a single revision.
      operationId: get/recommendationList/revision/get
      parameters:
      - description: Identifier of the revision.
        in: query
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        x-positive: true
      - description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
          set.
        explode: false
        in: query
        name: _attributes
        schema:
          items:
            maxLength: 100
            type: string
          maxItems: 50
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
        style: form
      - description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
        in: query
        name: _language
        schema:
          exclusiveMaximum: false
          exclusiveMinimum: false
          format: isoLanguage
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_2'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: Attributes of a single revision.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-accepts: application/json
  /recommendationList/revision/list:
    post:
      description: List of revisions of a recommendation list, excluding the elements
        of each revision.
      operationId: post/recommendationList/revision/list
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/inline_object'
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                data:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/_recommendationList_revision_list_data'
                meta:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/_recommendationList_revision_list_meta'
              required:
              - data
              type: object
              x-property-sort:
              - data
              - meta
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_3'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: List of revisions of a recommendation list.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-codegen-request-body-name: body
      x-contentType: application/json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /recommendationList/revision/search:
    get:
      description: Search for revisions of a recommendation list.
      operationId: get/recommendationList/revision/search
      parameters:
      - description: Restrict the search to revisions containing an element associated
          with the identified notation.
        in: query
        name: idNotation
        schema:
          format: id64
          type: string
          x-positive: true
        x-positive: true
      - description: Restrict the search to revisions pointing to the identified instrument.
        in: query
        name: idInstrument
        schema:
          format: id64
          type: string
          x-positive: true
        x-positive: true
      - description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
          set.
        explode: false
        in: query
        name: _attributes
        schema:
          items:
            maxLength: 100
            type: string
          maxItems: 50
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
        style: form
      - description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
        in: query
        name: _language
        schema:
          exclusiveMaximum: false
          exclusiveMinimum: false
          format: isoLanguage
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_4'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: Search for revisions of a recommendation list.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-accepts: application/json
  /recommendationList/revision/element/list:
    get:
      description: List of elements of a given revision.
      operationId: get/recommendationList/revision/element/list
      parameters:
      - description: Identifier of the revision.
        in: query
        name: idRevision
        required: true
        schema:
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        x-positive: true
      - description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
          set.
        explode: false
        in: query
        name: _attributes
        schema:
          items:
            maxLength: 100
            type: string
          maxItems: 50
          type: array
          uniqueItems: true
        style: form
      - description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
        in: query
        name: _language
        schema:
          exclusiveMaximum: false
          exclusiveMinimum: false
          format: isoLanguage
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_5'
          description: Successful Response
      summary: List of elements of a given revision.
      tags:
      - recommendationList
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsOffsetBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPaging: false
      x-supportsCursorBasedPagingWithoutTotal: false
      x-supportsPush: false
      x-requiresUser: false
      x-requiresInternalClient: false
      x-disallowUser: false
      x-no-merge: false
      x-maxSortParameterCount: 10
      x-supportsPermissionDeniedResponse: false
      x-accepts: application/json
components:
  requestBodies:
    inline_object:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_object'
      required: true
  responses:
    ErrorResponse:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            properties:
              meta:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorMetaObject'
              errors:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorObject'
            type: object
      description: Generic error response for all errors (400 ... 599 error codes)
  schemas:
    ErrorMetaObject:
      properties:
        status:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/StatusObject'
      type: object
    ErrorObject:
      description: The errors member contains additional information about a failed
        request.
      items:
        properties:
          details:
            description: A human-readable, unstructured explanation specific to this
              occurrence of the failure.
            type: string
          encryptedDetails:
            description: Base64-encoded, internal details about the error, in addition
              to "details".
            type: string
          type:
            description: Internal error type of the Foundation API protocol.
            format: int32
            type: number
          attribute:
            description: For a validation error, a reference to the request parameter
              that failed validation; otherwise, an empty array.
            items:
              properties:
                name:
                  description: Element of the path denoting the request parameter.
                  type: string
                index:
                  description: If the attribute "name" designates an array, index
                    of the array element; otherwise the special value -1.
                  format: int32
                  type: number
              type: object
              x-property-sort:
              - name
              - index
            type: array
        type: object
        x-property-sort:
        - detail
        - encryptedDetails
        - type
        - attribute
      type: array
    AttributesMember:
      description: Limit the attributes returned in the response to the specified
        set.
      items:
        maxLength: 100
        type: string
      maxItems: 50
      type: array
      uniqueItems: true
    LanguageMember:
      description: ISO 639-1 code of the language.
      exclusiveMaximum: false
      exclusiveMinimum: false
      format: isoLanguage
      maxLength: 2
      minLength: 2
      type: string
    StatusObject:
      description: The status member contains the status code of the response.
      example:
        code: 5.962133916683182
      properties:
        code:
          description: The HTTP status code of the response, mirroring the code from
            the Status-Line of the HTTP response message (see [RFC2616] section 6.1).
          format: int32
          type: number
      required:
      - code
      type: object
    CursorBasedPaginationOutputObject:
      description: Pagination attributes for the cursor-based pagination strategy.
      properties:
        total:
          description: Total number of entries in the result set.
          format: int32
          type: number
        isEstimatedTotal:
          description: Flag indicating that the value of `total` is estimated.
          type: boolean
        next:
          description: The next cursor position to use in the parameter `pagination.cursor`
            for an endpoint that supports cursor-based pagination, otherwise `null`.
          type: string
        previous:
          description: The previous cursor position to use in the parameter `pagination.cursor`
            for an endpoint that supports cursor-based pagination. If a previous cursor
            position is not supported or available, `previous` is `null`.
          type: string
      required:
      - isEstimatedTotal
      - next
      - previous
      - total
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - total
      - isEstimatedTotal
      - next
      - previous
    CursorBasedPaginationOutputObjectWithoutTotal:
      description: Pagination attributes for the cursor-based pagination strategy;
        a total element count is not supported.
      properties:
        next:
          description: The next cursor position to use in the parameter `pagination.cursor`
            for an endpoint that supports cursor-based pagination, otherwise `null`.
          type: string
        previous:
          description: The previous cursor position to use in the parameter `pagination.cursor`
            for an endpoint that supports cursor-based pagination. If a previous cursor
            position is not supported or available, `previous` is `null`.
          type: string
      required:
      - next
      - previous
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - next
      - previous
    OffsetBasedPaginationOutputObject:
      description: Pagination attributes for the offset-based pagination strategy.
      properties:
        total:
          description: Total number of entries in the result set.
          format: int32
          type: number
        isEstimatedTotal:
          description: Flag indicating that the value of "total" is estimated.
          type: boolean
      required:
      - isEstimatedTotal
      - total
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - total
      - isEstimatedTotal
    OffsetBasedPaginationOutputObjectWithoutTotal:
      description: Pagination attributes for the offset-based pagination strategy;
        a total element count is not supported.
      properties:
        hasNext:
          description: Flag indicating that a subsequent request with the same parameters,
            except that the parameter `pagination.offset` is incremented by `pagination.limit`,
            would yield additional results.
          type: boolean
      required:
      - hasNext
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - hasNext
    PartialOutputObject:
      description: Object denoting that the endpoint response is possibly incomplete.
      properties:
        isPartial:
          description: Flag indicating that the response is a possibly incomplete
            array or an object containing a possibly incomplete array, due to hitting
            a processing time limit. If `true`, some matching results might be missing
            from the array, or elements for matching results might be incorrectly
            included (for example, when priority sorting would have removed the element).
            Depending on the use case, such a response may be unsuitable.
          type: boolean
      required:
      - isPartial
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - isPartial
    inline_response_200_data_activeRange:
      description: Time range during which the recommendation list is, was, or will
        be active.
      example:
        start: start
        end: end
      properties:
        start:
          description: The starting point of the time range (inclusive), or `null`
            to indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the past.
          format: datetime
          type: string
        end:
          description: The ending point of the time range (exclusive), or `null` to
            indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the future.
          format: datetime
          type: string
      required:
      - end
      - start
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - start
      - end
    inline_response_200_data_activeRevision_activeRange:
      description: Time range during which the revision is, was, or will be active.
      example:
        start: start
        end: end
      properties:
        start:
          description: The starting point of the time range (inclusive), or `null`
            to indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the past.
          format: datetime
          type: string
        end:
          description: The ending point of the time range (exclusive), or `null` to
            indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the future.
          format: datetime
          type: string
      required:
      - end
      - start
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - start
      - end
    inline_response_200_data_activeRevision:
      description: Information on the active revision of this recommendation list,
        or null.
      example:
        activeRange:
          start: start
          end: end
        id: 1.4658129805029452
        title: title
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the currently active revision.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        title:
          description: The language specific name assigned to the recommendation list
            as of the given revision.
          format: localizedString
          type: string
        activeRange:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data_activeRevision_activeRange'
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - title
      - activeRange
    inline_response_200_data:
      description: Details about the recommendation list.
      example:
        activeRange:
          start: start
          end: end
        name: name
        id: 0.8008281904610115
        activeRevision:
          activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          id: 1.4658129805029452
          title: title
        numberRevisions: 6.027456183070403
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the recommendation list.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        name:
          description: Name of the recommendation list.
          type: string
        activeRange:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data_activeRange'
        numberRevisions:
          description: Number of all revisions of this recommendation list.
          format: int32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        activeRevision:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data_activeRevision'
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - name
      - activeRange
      - numberRevisions
      - activeRevision
    inline_response_200_meta:
      description: The meta member contains the meta information of the response.
      example:
        status:
          code: 5.962133916683182
      properties:
        status:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/StatusObject'
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - status
    inline_response_200:
      example:
        data:
          activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          name: name
          id: 0.8008281904610115
          activeRevision:
            activeRange:
              start: start
              end: end
            id: 1.4658129805029452
            title: title
          numberRevisions: 6.027456183070403
        meta:
          status:
            code: 5.962133916683182
      properties:
        data:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data'
        meta:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_meta'
      type: object
    inline_response_200_1_activeRange:
      description: Time range during which the recommendation list is active or has
        been active.
      example:
        start: start
        end: end
      properties:
        start:
          description: The starting point of the time range (inclusive), or `null`
            to indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the past.
          format: datetime
          type: string
        end:
          description: The ending point of the time range (exclusive), or `null` to
            indicate that the time range extends indefinitely into the future.
          format: datetime
          type: string
      required:
      - end
      - start
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - start
      - end
    inline_response_200_1_data:
      description: Recommendation list.
      example:
        activeRange:
          start: start
          end: end
        name: name
        id: 0.8008281904610115
        activeRevision:
          activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          id: 1.4658129805029452
          title: title
        numberRevisions: 6.027456183070403
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the recommendation list.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        name:
          description: Name of the recommendation list.
          type: string
        activeRange:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_1_activeRange'
        numberRevisions:
          description: Number of all revisions of this recommendation list.
          format: int32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        activeRevision:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data_activeRevision'
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - name
      - activeRange
      - numberRevisions
      - activeRevision
    inline_response_200_1:
      example:
        data:
        - activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          name: name
          id: 0.8008281904610115
          activeRevision:
            activeRange:
              start: start
              end: end
            id: 1.4658129805029452
            title: title
          numberRevisions: 6.027456183070403
        - activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          name: name
          id: 0.8008281904610115
          activeRevision:
            activeRange:
              start: start
              end: end
            id: 1.4658129805029452
            title: title
          numberRevisions: 6.027456183070403
        meta:
          status:
            code: 5.962133916683182
      properties:
        data:
          description: List of recommendation lists.
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_1_data'
          type: array
        meta:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_meta'
      type: object
    inline_response_200_2_data_recommendationList:
      description: The recommendation list to which this revision belongs.
      example:
        name: name
        id: 6.027456183070403
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the recommendation list.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        name:
          description: Name of the recommendation list.
          type: string
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - name
    inline_response_200_2_data_types:
      description: Type assigned to the recommendation list as of the given revision.
      example:
        name: name
        id: 1.4658129805029452
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the type.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        name:
          description: Name of the type.
          type: string
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - name
    inline_response_200_2_data_instrument:
      description: Instrument to which the recommendation list points, as of the given
        revision.
      example:
        id: id
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the instrument.
          format: id64
          type: string
          x-positive: true
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
    inline_response_200_2_data:
      description: Details about the revision.
      example:
        activeRange:
          start: start
          end: end
        types:
        - name: name
          id: 1.4658129805029452
        - name: name
          id: 1.4658129805029452
        description: description
        instrument:
          id: id
        id: 0.8008281904610115
        recommendationList:
          name: name
          id: 6.027456183070403
        title: title
      properties:
        id:
          description: Identifier of the revision.
          format: id32
          type: number
          x-positive: true
        recommendationList:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_2_data_recommendationList'
        types:
          description: Set of types assigned to the recommendation list as of the
            given revision. The customer maintains a list of valid types for all of
            its recommendation lists.
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_2_data_types'
          type: array
        title:
          description: Title assigned to the recommendation list as of the given revision.
          format: localizedString
          type: string
        description:
          description: Description assigned to the recommendation list as of the given
            revision.
          format: localizedString
          type: string
        activeRange:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_data_activeRevision_activeRange'
        instrument:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_response_200_2_data_instrument'
      type: object
      x-property-sort:
      - id
      - recommendationList
      - types
      - title
      - description
      - activeRange
      - instrument
    inline_response_200_2:
      example:
        data:
          activeRange:
            start: start
            end: end
          types:
          - name: name
            id: 1.4658129805029452
          - name: name
            id: 1.4658129805029452
          description: description
          instrument:
            id: id
          id: 0.8008281904610115
          recommendationList:
            name: name
            id: 6.027456183070403
